{"title":"来自农村的诗","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":12,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚，社里发出命令"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李学鳌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚，社里发出命令："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在结冻之前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把田里的菠菜铲净！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，像天河里涨了水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野上漂起无数星星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人影，锄光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锄光，人影。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在星际间如飞地奔跑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——挑一筐筐的菠菜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑一筐筐的歌声！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖界石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从大辩论的会场走出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张三下狠心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖掉了埋藏在地里和心里的界石！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“当初，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了给自己留后路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入社时我背着人埋下了你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了决心走社会主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要连根挖掉你！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1957年8月马召镇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文莽彦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党支书的笔记本是个大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把社员的意见都包容了下来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海为什么永远不会枯竭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为它和千万条江河从未分开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党支书的心是一个大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽阔深广，浩瀚无涯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家乡和祖国都住在他的心里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他心里还住着一个共产主义世界。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（江西进贤）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为他准备的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劲草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李么嫂赶场回家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买回新锄一把。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邻居二姑看见很奇怪："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你家锄头坏得这快？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"么嫂藏不住心头的高兴："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春娃的爸爸来了信！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要回家来下地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这锄头就是为他准备的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（贵州铜仁）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}